nodes.text: The RSF Intelligence Division was the intelligence branch of the Royal Naboo Security Forces.

Following the terrorist attack in the city of Theed, Intelligence Sergeant Bragg investigated the headquarters of the four major criminal organization on Naboo, namely the Skaak Tippers, Borvo the Hutt's criminal empire, the Darkwalkers and the Mummers. He discovered that the Mummers were responsible of the attack, leading to a RSF raid on the Mummer bunker.
